name: Handstand Pushups
description: With your feet up against the wall for balance, do deep handstand pushups so that your head can touch the ground.

name: Weighted Chin Ups
description: Weighted chin-ups are regular chin-ups but with additional weight either hanging from your waist with a dip belt, wearing a weighted vest, or holding a dumbbell between your legs.

name: Seated Shoulder Press
description: The seated dumbbell press is a variation of the standing dumbbell press and an exercise used to strengthen the muscles of the shoulders.

name: 3 Version Rows
description: Leaning rows at three angles; 90 degrees, 0 degrees, and back to the hip. Each targets a different part of the back.

name: Side-Front Raises
description: First, do all reps to the front, then do all reps to the side.

name: Leaning Fly Finisher
description: This exercise works well whether seated or standing, just make sure your back is straight and not strained.

name: Bulgarian Split Squat
description: The default distance from the foot rest is for you to be able to have a right angle bent knee when all the way down.

name: Single Leg RDL
description: RDL stands for Romanian Dead Lift. This exercise should target nearly your entire backside.

name: Sumo Squats
description: Make sure you target your outer buttocks muscles as you complete the motions.

name: Pistol Squats
description: Goal is to be able to do dragonfly squats.

name: Single Leg Hip Thrusts
description: Ideal distance from bench is to touch your heels while seated against the bench.

name: Single Leg Hip Thrusts
description: Ideal distance from bench is to touch your heels while seated against the bench.

name: Calf Raises
description: Best to do 3 angles of calf raises. The goal accounts for all three angles done consecutively.

name: One Arm Incline Pushups
description: You may need to spread your legs to maintain balance during the exercise.

name: Incline Dumbbell Curls
description: Do a slight incline. More is not better for the incline.

name: Incline Bench Press
description: Do a slight incline. More is not better for the incline.

name: Pinwheel Curls
description: Make sure you squeeze tight as to best work both targeted muscle groups here.

name: Incline Flys/pushups
description: Do as many pushups as you do flys, but immediately following the first exercise.
